'''''Bioscopia: Where Science Conquers Evil''''' (aka '''''Biolab''''') is a 2001 educational adventure video game. It is a sister game to ''[[Physicus]]'' and ''[[Chemicus]]''.
== Gameplay == Gameplay is similar to 1993 video game ''Myst''.
